<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="js" lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta content="width=device-width" name="viewport">
    <title>Add claim: Permanent Impairment | MyService</title>
    <link href="docs/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="uikit-body uikit-grid uikit-refactor">
    <noscript>
        <p role="alert">This website needs JavaScript to work properly.</p>
    </noscript>
    <nav class="uikit-skip-link">
        <a class="uikit-skip-link__link" href="#main-content">Skip to main content</a>
    </nav>
    <% include ../../../global/partials/header-topbar.ejs %>
        <% include ../../../global/partials/header-claims.ejs %>
            <% include ../partials/help-button.ejs %>
                <main>
                    <div id="main-content" class="section-feature border-bottom--mild margin-above--none margin-below--none padding-below">
                        <div class="container margin-above--none">
                            <h1 class="margin-above--none">
                                <span class="heading">Getting started</span>
                            </h1>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-8">

                                <h2 class="margin-above--large">When determining your level of Permanent Impairment compensation, we look at the effect your
                                    conditions have on your
                                    <b>lifestyle</b>.</h2>

                                <p class="margin-below--mid">The Lifestyle Questionnaire is your opportunity to
                                    <b>tell your story</b> and contribute to this decision. Base this on your worst day.</p>
                                <p class="margin-above--none">Alternatively, you can have DVA decide how your lifestyle has been affected by using medical
                                    reports already provided.</p>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <legend class="legend-label margin-below">Select an option to get started</legend>
                                    <div class="mys-radio-group">
                                        <label class="mys-radio">
                                            <input class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="home" value="no">
                                            <span class="mys-radio__box mys-radio__box--large">
                                                <img class="mys-radio__icon" src="../../../../docs/images/ico-message.svg">
                                                <span>Complete a Lifestyle Questionnaire</span>
                                            </span>
                                        </label>
                                        <label class="mys-radio">
                                            <input class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="home" value="yes-a-little">
                                            <span class="mys-radio__box mys-radio__box--large">
                                                <img class="mys-radio__icon" src="../../../../docs/images/ico-folder.svg">
                                                <span>Have DVA make a decision based on my medical reports.</span>
                                            </span>
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-sm-5">
                                        <p class="margin-above--mid margin-below--mid">Choose this option if:</p>
                                        <p>You want to
                                            <b>tell your story</b> based on your worst day of how your conditions have affected
                                            your lifestyle, and contribute to this decision.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-5">
                                        <p class="margin-above--mid margin-below--mid">Choose this option if:</p>
                                        <p>You want DVA to use your medical reports already provided to make the decision.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div> -->
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-8">
                                <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info margin-below--large" style="display:none;" id="lsq-pathway-tellstory--info">
                                    <p>When completing this questionnaire, take into consideration your accepted conditions.
                                        Refer to your 'Permanent Impairment Lifestyle Questionnaire' email to see what conditions
                                        are included.
                                    </p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="pagination">
                                    <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '/index-claims'">Back to Claims page</button>
                                    <div class="floated">
                                        <button class="uikit-btn btnNext" id="btnNext" onclick="window.location.href = '/pi-lsq-claim1'">Save and next</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>


                        <% include ../partials/cancel-modal.ejs %>
                    </div>

                </main>

                <% include ../../../global/partials/footer.ejs %>
                    <% include ../partials/panel-help.ejs %>

                        <script>

                            // Dynamic content for LSQ pathway
                            $("#lsq-pathway-tellstory").click(function () {
                                $("#lsq-pathway-tellstory--info").show();
                            });
                            $("#lsq-pathway-dvadoit").click(function () {
                                $("#lsq-pathway-tellstory--info").hide();
                            });
                        </script>

</body>

</html>